---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>Welcome to William Sutton's Blog</h1>
			<p>
				Hello, I'm William Sutton. Welcome to my blog, where I share my observations and conclusions on UK politics. This blog is dedicated to providing thoughtful analysis and commentary on the latest political events and trends within the United Kingdom.
			</p>
			<p>
				Through detailed examination and independent perspective, I aim to offer a unique viewpoint on current events and political issues. Whether it's breaking news or deep dives into policy and ideology, my goal is to present insights that are both engaging and thought-provoking.
			</p>
			<p>
				This blog serves as a platform for independent thought and discussion, free from the constraints of mainstream media narratives. I encourage readers to engage with the content, share their thoughts, and join me in exploring the complex world of UK politics.
			</p>
			<p>
				Feel free to explore the blog and check out the various articles and posts. If you have any questions or would like to engage in a discussion, don't hesitate to reach out.
			</p>
			<p>
				Thank you for visiting, and I hope you find the content both informative and stimulating.
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>